**Niquests** is a simple, yet elegant, HTTP library. It is a drop-in replacement for **Requests**, which is under feature freeze.

Niquests, is the â€œ**Safest**, **Fastest[^10]**, **Easiest**, and **Most advanced**â€ Python HTTP Client. Production Ready!

âœ”ï¸ **Try before you switch:** [See Multiplexed in Action](https://replit.com/@ahmedtahri4/Python#main.py)<br>
ğŸ“– **See why you should switch:** [Read about 10 reasons why](https://medium.com/@ahmed.tahri/10-reasons-you-should-quit-your-http-client-98fd4c94bef3), and ["_Revived the promise made six years ago for Requests 3_"](https://medium.com/@ahmed.tahri/revived-the-promise-made-six-years-ago-for-requests-3-37b440e6a064)<br>
âœ¨ **You were used to betamax, requests-mock, responses, ...?** [See how they still work! We got you covered.](https://niquests.readthedocs.io/en/latest/community/extensions.html)

